      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a collector's dream. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, showroom-quality shine and no imperfections, while the interior is immaculate and retains its original factory freshness. Every mechanical component has been meticulously maintained to ensure it performs exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot. Buyers can expect a car that needs nothing but a driver who appreciates perfection.",
